'''Zap Gangs''' were [[Human/Legends|Humans]] that roamed [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] dangerous [[Coruscant Underworld/Legends|Undercity]]. [[Alema Rar]] encountered one such gang while stalking [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]]. The gang was bullying a [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Gender/Legends|female]], pushing her against the safety rail of a bridge. Alema [[Mind trick/Legends|Force persuaded]] the gang to allow the Gamorrean push them, keeping the [[Cosmic Balance]].

